snippet.title: Official Luna Online: Reborn Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome one and all to the official re-birth of Luna Online!  

Explore an enchanting world full of adventure, mystery and humor!  Build a home, run a farm, raise livestock, and even start your own family!

Dodge lightning bolts from the sky as you slay down mighty dragons, or go to a quiet spot to fish. What meal will you catch today?  

Form a mighty circle of friends and build your own Guild Halls, participate in raids and PvP combat as you face off against other guilds in weekly competitions.  Who will gain control of Luna Castle?

Check us out today at: www.subagames.com and luna.subagames.com

Music by: www.bensound.com
